data.description: You'll have plenty of room to spread out in this beautiful home located in Midway ISD! You'll love the generous floor plan that includes a downstairs living area with a towering walls of windows that flows to the kitchen accented with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances as well as a formal dining area, breakfast area, and a 1/2 bath for guests. The master suite includes dual vanities, separate tub/shower, and a generous walk in closet that is sure to please! Upstairs includes 3 bedrooms, a full bath, and a loft area perfect for a second living area or game room. Complete with covered back patio area and privacy fenced yard, this home is one you will love for years to come!
